Package: DatabaseLinke.R
Title: DatabaseLinke.R – Parse, open, save, links to databases and search
    engines from your list of gene symbols
Version: 1.8.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Abel", "Vertesy", , "av@imba.oeaw.ac.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions to parse and open (search query) links to
    genomics related and other websites for R. Useful when you want to
    explore e.g.: the function of a set of differentially expressed genes.
